---
title: Tangy Sesame Chicken with Fragrant Jasmine Rice
description: This take on the classic Chinese take-out mainstay is for you sweet-and -sour lovers out there! Paired with soy-ginger veggies and fragrant rice, this dish will make you think twice about ordering Chinese take-out again!
